{"tid":1852731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外界批評口罩太貴 台灣宣布降價！ 二月起降至6元","createTime":"2020-01-30T14:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T14:50:45.000Z","uid":209657,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97aea3181999c75c0994ae8e8c9532e78ac20198","tid":1852731,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"經濟部、衛福部近日透過超商釋出戰備口罩，但外界有聲音批評每副8元價格太貴，經濟部今也宣布下修，至2月1日起將降為每副6元、3副18元。而府院今也宣布徵用口罩統一調度，經濟部表示徵用口罩將先分配醫療、公務使用、每日140萬副，接著向超商或醫療院所附近藥局、藥妝釋出260萬片，每人仍限購3片、實施到2月15日。"},{"pid":"15fdfc6125db625b026fe51fc900f2f969f890fa","tid":1852731,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:48:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3052958?fbclid=IwAR3DD4KzK9fXSSwz80I6otlcbGLfGf7ViZfdY1aHSuFU8jwzgvH9jSlnB_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3052958%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3DD4KzK9fXSSwz80I6otlcbGLfGf7ViZfdY1aHSuFU8jwzgvH9jSlnB_s&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=764bbc05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3052958%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3DD4KzK9fXSSwz80I6otlcbGLfGf7ViZfdY1aHSuFU8jwzgvH9jSlnB_s&h=673fa225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3052958?fbclid=IwAR3DD4KzK9fXSSwz80I6otlcbGLfGf7ViZfdY1aHSuFU8jwzgvH9jSlnB_s</a>"},{"pid":"1b37013ed97423a96ffdd8e9079d9b4dce1706b2","tid":1852731,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97aea3181999c75c0994ae8e8c9532e78ac20198","tid":1852731,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"經濟部、衛福部近日透過超商釋出戰備口罩，但外界有聲音批評每副8元價格太貴，經濟部今也宣布下修，至2月1日起將降為每副6元、3副18元。而府院今也宣布徵用口罩統一調度，經濟部表示徵用口罩將先分配醫療、公務使用、每日140萬副，接著向超商或醫療院所附近藥局、藥妝釋出260萬片，每人仍限購3片、實施到2月15日。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"六蚊＝HKD1.5，差唔多"},{"pid":"6025df396a98ab9e93fdb3dad71ecdc18afa87a8","tid":1852731,"u